        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A *composer staff* is short and shaped like an elegant black conductor's baton with a silver tip. When waved through the air, it hums melodically. In this way, you can play it as though it were an instrument, and it grants a +1 item bonus to Performance checks made with it.",
